text: The elm cultivar Ulmus × hollandica 'Odin' is one of five miniature or bonsai cultivars from the Elegantissima Group raised by the Gartneriet Vestdal nursery in Odense, Denmark. ==Description== 'Odin' is distinguished by its light-green leaves and their irregular margins. ==Nurseries== ===Europe=== Gartneriet Vestdal , Odense, Denmark.
